{"title_page": "Witthawin Klorwuttiwat", "text_new": "{{Unreferenced|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Witthawin Klorwuttiwat\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Witthawin Klorwuttiwat\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1991|08|29|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Chonburi]], [[Thailand]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| currentclub    = [[Lamphun Warrior F.C.|Lamphun Warrior]]\n| clubnumber     = 23\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]]\n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| years1         = 2013\n| clubs1         = [[Pattaya United F.C.|Pattaya United]]\n| caps1          = 1\n| goals1         = 0\n| years2         = 2013\u20132015\n| clubs2         = [[Chainat F.C.|Chainat]]\n| caps2          = 0\n| goals2         = 0\n| years3         = 2016\n| clubs3         = [[Sukhothai F.C.|Sukhothai]] \n| caps3          = 1\n| goals3         = 0\n| years4         = 2017\u20132019\n| clubs4         = [[Nongbua Pitchaya F.C.|Nongbua Pitchaya]] \n| caps4          = \n| goals4         = \n| years5         = 2020\u2013\n| clubs5         = [[Lamphun Warrior F.C.|Lamphun Warrior]]\n| caps5          =  \n| goals5         = \n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  = [[Thailand national under-17 football team|Thailand U17]]\n| nationalcaps1  = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| nationalyears2 = 2009\u20132010\n| nationalteam2  = [[Thailand national under-20 football team|Thailand U19]]\n| nationalcaps2  = \n| nationalgoals2 = \n| nationalyears3 = 2009\u20132015\n| nationalteam3  = [[Thailand national under-23 football team|Thailand U23]]\n| nationalcaps3  = \n| nationalgoals3 = \n| pcupdate       = \n| ntupdate       = \n}}\n\n'''Witthawin Klorwuttiwat''' ({{lang-th|\u0e27\u0e34\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\u0e17\u0e23\u0e4c \u0e04\u0e25\u0e2d\u0e27\u0e38\u0e12\u0e34\u0e27\u0e31\u0e12\u0e19\u0e4c}}, born August 29, 1991), is a Thai professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]] for [[Thai League 3]] club [[Lamphun Warrior F.C.|Lamphun Warrior]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|1}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|287558}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://player.7mth.com/306060/index.shtml|website=player.7mth.com|title=\u0e27\u0e34\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\u0e17\u0e23\u0e4c \u0e04\u0e25\u0e2d\u0e27\u0e38\u0e12\u0e34\u0e27\u0e31\u0e12\u0e19\u0e4c (Wittawin Clowuttiwat) \u0e02\u0e49\u0e2d\u0e21\u0e39\u0e25\u0e19\u0e31\u0e01\u0e1f\u0e38\u0e15\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e25|accessdate=2020-04-04}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://all7m.com/%e0%b8%a5%e0%b8%b3%e0%b8%9e%e0%b8%b9%e0%b8%99-%e0%b8%84%e0%b8%a7%e0%b9%89%e0%b8%b2-%e0%b8%a7%e0%b8%b4%e0%b8%98%e0%b8%a7%e0%b8%b4%e0%b8%99%e0%b8%97%e0%b8%a3%e0%b9%8c-%e0%b8%ad/|title=\u0e25\u0e33\u0e1e\u0e39\u0e19 \u0e04\u0e27\u0e49\u0e32 \"\u0e27\u0e34\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\u0e17\u0e23\u0e4c\" \u0e2d\u0e14\u0e35\u0e15\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e31\u0e07\u0e40\u0e22\u0e32\u0e27\u0e0a\u0e19\u0e17\u0e35\u0e21\u0e0a\u0e32\u0e15\u0e34\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e34\u0e21\u0e41\u0e01\u0e23\u0e48\u0e07 &#124; \u0e1a\u0e49\u0e32\u0e19\u0e1c\u0e25\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e25&#124; \u0e17\u0e35\u0e40\u0e14\u0e47\u0e14 &#124; \u0e14\u0e39\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e25 &#124; \u0e1c\u0e25\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e25|website=all7m.com|accessdate=2020-04-04}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Klorwuttiwat, Witthawin}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Thai footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Sukhothai F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Thai League 1 players]]\n[[Category:Thailand youth international footballers]]\n\n\n{{Thailand-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Witthawin Klorwuttiwat\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Witthawin Klorwuttiwat\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1991|08|29|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Chonburi]], [[Thailand]]\n| height         = {{height|m=1