[Oridathoru Phayalvaan]]''\n* 1982: Kualalumpur Film Festival \u2013 Best Script \u2013 ''[[Oridathoru Phayalvaan]]''\n* 1982: Gulf Award for Best Film \u2013 ''[[Novemberinte Nashtam]]''\n* 1983: Pournami Award for Best Director \u2013 ''[[Koodevide]]''\n* 1987: Film Chamber Award for Best Story \u2013 ''[[Thoovanathumbikal]]''\n* 1988: Film Fare Award for Best Director \u2013 ''[[Aparan (film)|Aparan]]''\n* 1990: Film Chamber Award for Best Story \u2013 ''[[Innale]]''\n* 1991: FAC award \u2013 ''[[Njan Gandharvan]]''\n\n==Padmarajan Award==\n{{Main|Padmarajan Award}}\nPadmarajan Puraskaram or Padmarajan Award is an annual film/literary award instituted by the Padmarajan Memorial Trust.<ref name=\"2009awards\">[http://www.hindu.com/2010/04/15/stories/2010041553270500.htm Padmarajan Puraskaram for writer Paul Zachariah]. ''[[The Hindu]]''. April 4, 2010. Retrieved July 15, 2015.</ref> It carries a plaque and a cash award of {{INR}} 10,000.<ref name=\"2009awards\"/> The award is given in two categories:\n\n*Padmarajan Award for Best Short Story\n*Padmarajan Award for Best Film\n\n==See also==\n* [[Malayalam cinema]]\n* [[Bharathan]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name | id = 0655802}}\n* {{official|http://www.padmarajan.com/ }}\n*[http://www.cinemaofmalayalam.net/padmarajan.html cinemaofmalayalam.net]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20130604082145/http://www.mathrubhumi.com/books/article/memories/2373/ An excerpt from ''Padmarajan: Ente Gandharvan'' by Radhalakshmi] (in Malayalam)\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20130604093347/http://www.mathrubhumi.com/books/article/memories/2283/ An article by ''Mathrubhumi'' during the silver jubilee of ''Aparan'']\n\n{{Padmarajan}}\n{{Malayalam Literature |state=collapsed}}\n{{Filmfare Award Best Malayalam Director}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:1945 births]]\n[[Category:1991 deaths]]\n[[Category:Malayalam film directors]]\